high_descs: Go straight, then make a left at the sink and face the sink.
Take the black mug from the sink.
Turn right and go to the oven.
Put the mug in the microwave, turn on the microwave, take the mug from the microwave.
Turn left and face towards the coffee maker.
Put the mug on the coffee maker platform.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm mug on the coffee maker.

high_descs: Grab the black cup from the sink
Turn right, walk to the stove
Open the microwave, put the cup in the microwave, close the microwave, turn on the microwave, open the microwave, take the cup out, close the microwave
Turn left, walk to the coffee machine
Put the cup in the coffee machine
anns.task_desc: Heat the cup with microwave, put the cup in the coffee machine

high_descs: Turn left and walk towards the sink.
Pick up the cup from the inside of the sink.
Turn left, head towards the stove, and look up to the microwave.
Put the cup in the microwave, heat it, and pick the cup back out.
Turn left and look at the coffee maker on the counter.
Place the cup on the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Warm up the cup from the sink to put on the coffee maker.
